<l>īreḻut torumoḻi yuyirttoṭa riṭaittoṭa</l>
<l>rāytat toṭarmoḻi vaṉṟoṭar meṉṟoṭa</l>
<l>rāyiru mūṉṟē yukaraṅ kuṟukiṭaṉ</l>
